By PAMELA LEWIS  
 Long Beach Press Telegram  
<TEXT>
<P>
   INGLEWOOD, Calif. _ The Los Angeles Sparks look to extend their
winning streak to 12 games today when they face the Utah Starzz at
5 p.m. at the Forum.
</P>
<P>
