<HEADLINE>
DELAHOUSSAYE'S TOUGH RIDE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(HOLLYWOOD GOLD CUP SIDEBAR) 
By KEVIN MODESTI  
 c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   INGLEWOOD, Calif. _ Eddie Delahoussaye's legendary calm is being
seriously tested these days.
</P>
<P>
   This afternoon's $1 million Hollywood Gold Cup, in which
Delahoussaye will ride Out of Mind, is the easy part for the Hall
of Fame jockey.
</P>
<P>
   Monday morning, he'll watch his wife Juanita go into the
hosp}TG &Cx1f; RIw6''rgery to repair an aneurysm near her brain. It is
